Fleming Family May Invest $2 Billion in Russian Iron, RIA Says

-- B y   Y u l i y a   F e d o r i n o v a
-- 
2011-08-22T11:28:23Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-22/fleming-family-may-invest-2-billion-in-russian-iron-ria-says.html
Fleming Family & Partners, a U.K.
private equity firm, may invest $2 billion to develop iron ore
deposits in the Chelyabinsk region of  Russia , RIA Novosti
reported, citing local Governor Mikhail Yurevich.  Tatiana Kazantseva, a Moscow-based spokeswoman of Fleming
Family, declined to comment on the report when Bloomberg called.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Yuliya Fedorinova in Moscow at 
 yfedorinova@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
